Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why dominoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These have nothing to do\Nwith being an astronaut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's no good. This is complete nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's in this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use all of the dominoes in the boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make a domino line ready to be toppled\Nwithin the seven days allotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? With all of these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to\Nmake us do with this exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They want to make us line up dominoes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lion-san told me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The most important qualities\Nfor an astronaut to have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are perseverance and a\Ncooperative spirit, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They must be trying to test those here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this thing\Nhas gotten to you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just got a little fun for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Fun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi, you really are a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's no need to apologize, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think this is going to be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably just time for\Nlights out, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? If that's all, they should say\Nso before turning out the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then... Asumi, where do you wanna sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with whichever is\Nleft after you two choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, sorry, but could you\Nlet me take the bottom bunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really bad about sleeping in high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, she could at least answer us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dunno how to put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but these beds are so compressed that\Nit's almost hard to breathe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know, we still haven't heard her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be hard to ask now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we just give her a nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... her hairpin is cute,\Nso how about Pinko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pinko?! That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything else we could use?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukita Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Then, how should we address you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever. You can use my family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you mean when you said that there\Nwas no way that you would be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, you didn't hesitate at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, all of the numbers written\Non the rooms are distances to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is the distance to my favorite star...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The distance do Spica, which\NLion-san told me long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}350 light years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, I found Spica!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow. Very well done, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's out there, 350 light years away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Shining so beautifully that\Nit was also known as the "pearl star."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the alpha star in the constellation Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's a secret behind that star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, Spica isn't just one star,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's something called a binary star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Binary star?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, a binary star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two stars rotate around, chasing\Neach other at incredible speeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so if you look at it from as far away as Earth,\Nthey look like one big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyhow, their rotation speed is so high that\Nthe stars aren't perfectly circular,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but actually oval-shaped instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The twin Spicas support each other\Nto give birth to that radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll continue on and on like\Nthat until one of them disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that explanation too difficult for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lion-san, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You aren't going to disappear\Nand go off anywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll always, always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah. I won't be going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as there are stars up there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like I'm a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Come on, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's morning, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you sleep-talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, stand up! Let's go wash your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can walk by myself, Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just come with me. One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ukita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She really does rub me the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The least she could do is properly greet us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's just shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? She's just a contrary neat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukita-san just kind of reminds\Nme of someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend I used to play with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the atmosphere about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasane-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand how she felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I ended up hurting her very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:10:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We ended up going separate ways, so I don't\Nknow what she's doing now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think I could understand\Nher a little bit better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not with words, but with feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, it may just be coincidence that we\Nended up together, but since we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be friends with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-san, and Ukita-san both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's have breakfast and\Nget started on those dominoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or so I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But looking at how many there are,\NI can't help but feel a little depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the paper that had the\Nproject procedures written on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use all of the dominoes in the boxes\Nto make a domino line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ready to be toppled within the seven days allotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are free to line them up however you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there should be one line\Nconnecting the start and finish points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, within seven days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we're supposed to\Ndo if we finish before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't give us a project\Nthat we would finish too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, there might be\Nsomething written in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that seven days is\Na long time for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means that there must be something\Nthat won't let us finish in seven days?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like there is\Nanything else written about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we should just\Ngive it a shot, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, it looks like we can manuallly\Npush that box into the wall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times does that make, Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was because we thought that might happen\Nthat we're lining them up separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we're making them into one long line later,\Nwe'll have to be more careful, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But really, I wish they had at least\Ngiven us some stoppers too. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this much done, it's looking more like we might\Nget that break that you were talking about, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't as big of a deal as I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is so irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to tediously line up dominoes,\Nclosed up in a room with just us three guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to do these\Ntedious little projects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here to do something bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, you've been really obnoxious lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get working on this some more, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's a moron, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You with the monk haircut over there, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what will\Nhappen if you get me mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can have you all drop out alongside\Nme with a push of this button, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is it, Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't have any mercy\Nbeating the crap out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a joke, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get all scary like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get so serious about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suzuki, why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can call me Shuu, Fuchuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, why did you want to get into this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to call me Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stop working, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone wants to go into space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Right?" Who are we talking about, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then why did you want\Nto come here, Fuchuuya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be a little seagull\Nthat's the surprising reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me, it would have to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photo that Armstrong took\Nof the first moon landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got the feeling that I was\Non the moon myself from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I was pretty moved by it, even as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buzz Aldrin, standing at the\Nedge of a small crater...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humanity's first step...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pale blue Earth floating above the horizon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my personality, looking at it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that I'd love to take my own picture\Nof the Earth just floating up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's my motive, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... Going to space has been a dream\Nof mine ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rocket driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call it a pilot, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone else told me the same thing once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most people would say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, how about you, Ukita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to get into this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please be quiet now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You happen to talk a lot in your sleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not bothered by a little talking in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I really do talk a lot in my sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, it's nothing to worry about, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Compared to your nocturnal\Ntooth grinding, it's pretty cute, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi, do I grind my teeth at night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do it a little bit, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's "a little bit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the first time anyone's told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shock! I can never get married now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to be quiet already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally halfway done, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, that was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I think that they gave us seven days because\Nthey figured that things like this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now that four days have passed,\Nthis really has gotten annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know what the weather is like outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I feel like the pilot who\Nasked them to put a window in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what meaning is there\Nto doing this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's useless to think there's\Nany kind of meaning to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just an overly difficult project that they're using to\Nweed people out since there were so many applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are a dry woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As parched as the Gobi Desert, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I should say something earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but would you start addressing me by name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then what do you want me to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I call you Lady Marika or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You neat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you cool your head off a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only called you a neat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say that once more, why don't you?\NI won't let you off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say it as many times as I want,\Nyou neat-freak neat-freak neat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}First off, whose fault do you think it was\Nthat we had to do that all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? We should all be after the same dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wasn't the only one to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't group us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dominoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ou-Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My head feels so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs are going numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My vision too... What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sick... This is not normal at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a test, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll calm down in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What basis do you have for saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we won't!\NI won't put up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made your teeth hurt and made you feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all of our carefully lined up\Ndominoes... gone in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They probably did a sudden\Ndecompression of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sudden decompression? An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is another part of the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A test? This?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of collisions between spaceships\Nand debris has been increasing each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not unthinkable for there to be a major\Naccident sometime in the future anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Space garbage, like abandoned\Nsatellites and parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I know that much at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't keep yourself together,\Neven under those circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you have no business going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter how you look at it,\Nthat's going a little too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh man, why are you shaking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!\NCome on, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mo... ther...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone... died...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
